title: Keeping Positive & Beating Cancer w/ Hal Elrod
itunes:title: Keeping Positive & Beating Cancer w/ Hal Elrod
description:
Episode 342 - Hal Elrod has died once. Now he can say he beat cancer. Recently cancer free, Hal takes us through what it was like to be diagnosed with cancer and how he only accepted that he had cancer but also remained extremely positive while fighting it. This is my favorite interview I have done to date, I can't wait for you to listen to it!
